0xCE8E25B4.name: MUMBLE_SET_VOLUME_OVERRIDE_BY_SERVER_ID

params.name: volume
params.description: The volume, ranging from 0.0 to 1.0 (or above).

0xCE8E25B4.description: Overrides the output volume for a particular player with the specified server id and player name on Mumble. This will also bypass 3D audio and distance calculations. -1.0 to reset the override.
